大眾媒體對於凱爾普遍給予正面的印象，如遊戲資訊網站[[IGN|IGN]]表示凱爾就是你腦海裡的典型、一絲不苟、強健的美國硬漢，並覺得往後《快打旋風》若是再次改編電影，仍需要選擇凱爾作為挑起劇情大樑的角色。<ref name="IGN">{{cite web |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2009/02/18/top-25-street-fighters-the-final-five?page=4 |title=Top 25 Street Fighters: The Final Five |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |author=D. F. Smith |date=2012-06-16 |accessdate=2020-08-14 |archive-date=2018-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930052352/https://www.ign.com/articles/2009/02/18/top-25-street-fighters-the-final-five?page=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2008/06/03/franchise-reboot-videogame-heroes?page=4 |title=Franchise Reboot: Videogame Heroes |work=IGN |author=Jesse Schedeen |date=2008-06-04 |accessdate=2020-08-14 |archive-date=2018-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180925214529/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/06/03/franchise-reboot-videogame-heroes?page=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>線上媒體UGO Networks則認為凱爾是《快打旋風》系列裡除了[[隆|隆]]跟[[肯·馬斯達斯|肯]]之外，最重要的角色之一。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ugo.com/games/top-50-street-fighter-characters?page=4 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100828102817/http://www.ugo.com/games/top-50-street-fighter-characters?page=4 |dead-url=yes |title=Top 50 Street Fighter Characters |work=UGO Networks |author=Paul Furfari |date=2010-08-25 |archive-date=2010-08-28 |accessdate=2020-08-14 }}</ref>

在遊戲裡凱爾的格鬥風格，多視為適合偏好防禦策略玩家使用的角色。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/gamesblog/2009/feb/20/playstation-xbox |title=A beginner's guide to Street Fighter IV |work=[[衛報|衛報]] |author=Keith Stuart |date=2009-02-20 |accessdate=2020-08-14 |archive-date=2019-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909051022/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/gamesblog/2009/feb/20/playstation-xbox |dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[衛報|衛報]]》提及凱爾的格鬥風格反應出他的強悍性格，就是一邊使用可朝遠距離攻擊的{{nihongo|「音速爆擊」|ソニックブーム}}牽制對手，一邊耐心等待著對手迎面而來，當你一被搞到煩躁起來，就會落入他的陷阱。<ref name="TheGuardian">{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/gamesblog/2010/apr/28/top-20-street-fighter-characters |title=Ryan Hart's top 20 Street Fighter characters – Part 1 |work=衛報 |author=Keith Stuart |date=2010-04-29 |accessdate=2020-08-14 |archive-date=2019-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629201204/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/gamesblog/2010/apr/28/top-20-street-fighter-characters |dead-url=no }}</ref>網路漫畫平台8-Bit Theater的創建者布萊恩·克萊文格（Brian Clevinger）則形容凱爾有如「《[[孫子兵法|孫子兵法]]》中所討論一切的縮影」。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nuklearpower.com/daily.php?date=051027 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080413142858/http://www.nuklearpower.com/daily.php?date=051027 |title=Episode 617: Thinking Ahead |work=Nuklear Power |author=Brian Clevinger |date=2005-10-27 |archive-date=2008-04-13 |accessdate=2020-08-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

凱爾頭頂類似掃把的豎起髮型模樣，有被遊戲雜誌《GameDaily》視為是電子遊戲界裡最稀奇的髮型之一，並對於在《快打旋風》改編電影當中，飾演凱爾的尚-克勞德·范·達美沒有忠實呈現此模樣一事感到可惜。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/galleries/weirdest-hairstyles-in-gaming/?page=13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090415220102/http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/galleries/weirdest-hairstyles-in-gaming/?page=13 |dead-url=yes |title=Weirdest Hairstyles In Gaming |work=GameDaily |archive-date=2009-04-15 |accessdate=2020-08-14 }}</ref>

